original_title: TJP Brand New Wrestling 2 Now It's Time To Attack
overview: Tokyo Joshi Pro Wrestling runs its third Korakuen Hall show of 2018 this Saturday 25 August, entitled “Brand New Wrestling 2 ~ Now It’s Time to Attack ~”. The event will be streaming live on DDT Universe starting at 10am UK time. For anybody out there that isn’t already firmly on board the TJP bandwagon, this is a primer of sorts.
title: TJP Brand New Wrestling 2 Now It's Time To Attack
